{"tid":994010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真・香港人極需要一個全新身份","createTime":"2019-01-24T10:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T13:34:57.000Z","uid":36058,"like":23,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"349264565237e87a2bf5c43bf3c7e092e01865c4","tid":994010,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T10:58:35.000Z","msg":"好感慨，突然發現連街邊中學雞都講蝗語，以前得小學蝗，而家已蔓延中學，佢地拎住香港人身份招搖撞騙，好心噏。<br />\n<br />\n忽發奇想，要建立土生土長香港人嘅身份以區別之。當外國人問起Where are you from時，我可以理直氣壯咁講。暫時諗到係British Hong Kong，因為九七前出世。如果大家同意，可否統一口徑，以後外國人面前都咁講。唔好再講Hong Kong。<br />\n<br />\n或者有冇其他人有更好身份名稱？"},{"pid":"61e05e5f866561e94cb9469574cee8fea6d3147b","tid":994010,"uid":36058,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T11:09:03.000Z","msg":"新腥港人根本就應該叫香特人或大灣區人，但佢哋僭奪咗香港人身份。<br />\n<br />\n港英遺民可以選擇：<br />\n<br />\n1. 融入香特人或大灣區人<br />\n2. 寧死不從，自建身份<br />\n<br />\n移民都冇用，人哋會問where are you originally from。"},{"pid":"61dc3ee423dc8cca8f174a70166dcfb7dc7ab328","tid":994010,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T11:17:31.000Z","msg":"香特蝗偷偷留下負評"},{"pid":"5fd28779a7dc906f2a5e68419311fcfc58b5e729","tid":994010,"uid":207702,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T11:35:39.000Z","msg":"番到中學除左班中6同中5 全部都講蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe5039b24475b687e049be004d4a44aae207827","tid":994010,"uid":43428,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T12:48:46.000Z","msg":"蝗國人"},{"pid":"4ae146b77a795d1eb8cedb3b4fee7552ff9d8c87","tid":994010,"uid":183758,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"I'm from Free Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\n我來自自由香港."},{"pid":"513567cc0b8de0d0da663812992a0dbc753153df","tid":994010,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ae146b77a795d1eb8cedb3b4fee7552ff9d8c87","tid":994010,"uid":183758,"like":